msgctxt "6980"
msgid "ちぇっちぇ、なんだよなんだよー！"
msgstr "Hey, what is it!"

msgctxt "7013"
msgid "みんなしてオレのことのけ者にしてさあ！"
msgstr "Let's all make me an outcast!"

msgctxt "7052"
msgid "オレだって……　オレだって……"
msgstr "Even me ... Even me ..."

msgctxt "7083"
msgid "オレだってさあ！"
msgstr "Come on me!"

msgctxt "7110"
msgid "ひゃ、こ……　殺さないで！"
msgstr "Hey, this ... don't kill me!"

msgctxt "7137"
msgid "……お前、ひとをなんだと思ってるんだ？"
msgstr "...... What do you think you are?"

msgctxt "7176"
msgid "あ、ご、ごごごめんなさい……"
msgstr "Oh, I'm sorry ..."

msgctxt "7205"
msgid "“オレだって”……なんだ？"
msgstr "\"Even I\" ... what?"

msgctxt "7232"
msgid "えっ……"
msgstr "eh……"

msgctxt "7241"
msgid ""
"何かひとりで言っていただろう。\n"
"“オレだって”……　と。"
msgstr "I would have said something alone. \"Even I\" ..."

msgctxt "7298"
msgid "……あっ！"
msgstr "……Ah!"

msgctxt "7309"
msgid ""
"……言いたくないならいい。\n"
"邪魔したな。"
msgstr "...... If you don't want to say it. I disturbed you."

msgctxt "7351"
msgid "オレだって……　みんなと遊びたいんだ……！"
msgstr "Even I ... I want to play with everyone ...!"

msgctxt "7409"
msgid ""
"……それでさぁ、うちの親きびしくてさぁ！\n"
"かざぐるまとか、シャボン玉とか、ベーゴマとか、\n"
"みんなが持ってるおもちゃ買ってもらえなくてさぁ！"
msgstr ""
"…… So, let's get close to our parents! You can't buy toys that everyone has,"
" such as pinwheels, soap bubbles, and beigoma!"

msgctxt "7548"
msgid ""
"オレらのまわりじゃさ、\n"
"みんなと同じもの持ってるってことが\n"
"すごく大事なんだよ！"
msgstr ""
"Around us, it's very important to have the same things as everyone else!"

msgctxt "7629"
msgid ""
"でもうちの親、わかってないからさぁ……\n"
"やんなっちゃうよ！"
msgstr "But my parents don't know, so ... I'm gonna do it!"

msgctxt "7688"
msgid "なるほど、子供の世界もいろいろ大変だな。"
msgstr "I see, the world of children is also difficult."

msgctxt "7729"
msgid ""
"そーなんだよ、今日だってさぁ！\n"
"みんなでベーゴマするってのに、\n"
"オレだけ、持ってなくてさぁ……！"
msgstr ""
"That's right, even today! Even though everyone is beigoma, I don't have it "
"...!"

msgctxt "7826"
msgid "……それで、ひとりでふてくされてたのか。"
msgstr "...... So, did you get rid of yourself?"

msgctxt "7867"
msgid "……うん。"
msgstr "……Yup."

msgctxt "7878"
msgid ""
"うーむ、子供の世界はよくわからんが、\n"
"みんなと同じおもちゃを持ってるっていうのが\n"
"そんなに大事なことなのか？"
msgstr ""
"Hmmm, I don't really understand the world of children, but is it so "
"important to have the same toys as everyone else?"

msgctxt "7987"
msgid ""
"そりゃそうだよ……\n"
"だって、ベーゴマ持ってないと\n"
"みんなと一緒にベーゴマで遊べないじゃないか。"
msgstr ""
"That's right ... Because if you don't have a beigoma, you can't play with "
"everyone in a beigoma."

msgctxt "8082"
msgid "そんなことはないと思うがな。"
msgstr "I don't think that's the case."

msgctxt "8111"
msgid "えー……　うそだよ。"
msgstr "Eh ... it's a lie."

msgctxt "8132"
msgid ""
"ベーゴマがなくても……\n"
"例えば審判をするだとか、友達を応援するだとか、\n"
"みんなで一緒にいることを楽しむことはできるだろ？"
msgstr ""
"Even if you don't have a beigoma ... For example, you can referee, cheer on "
"your friends, and enjoy being together?"

msgctxt "8253"
msgid "うーん……"
msgstr "Hmm ..."

msgctxt "8264"
msgid ""
"それに、おもちゃがなければ\n"
"友達から借りたらいいじゃないか。\n"
"……なぜそれをしない？"
msgstr ""
"Besides, if you don't have toys, why not borrow one from a friend? ...... "
"Why don't you do it?"

msgctxt "8349"
msgid ""
"それは、だって……\n"
"オレ、友達に貸せるもの持ってないんだもん……"
msgstr "That's because ... I don't have anything to lend to my friends ..."

msgctxt "8414"
msgid ""
"お互いにタイトウなカンケーじゃないと、\n"
"友達って言えないんだぞ！"
msgstr "You can't say that you're friends unless you're both tight-knit!"

msgctxt "8479"
msgid "……ずいぶん難しい言葉を知っているな。"
msgstr "...... I don't know very difficult words."

msgctxt "8518"
msgid ""
"オレも何か友達に貸せるもの、ひとつでも持ってれば\n"
"おもちゃの貸し借りとかできるのになぁ……"
msgstr ""
"I can lend something to my friends, and if I have at least one, I can lend "
"and borrow toys ..."

msgctxt "8609"
msgid "……そうだ！　おっちゃん！"
msgstr "……That's it! Uncle!"

msgctxt "8636"
msgid "お、おっちゃん……"
msgstr "Oh, uncle ..."

msgctxt "8655"
msgid ""
"おっちゃんが持ってるいらないもの、\n"
"オレにくれないかな？"
msgstr "Can you give me something you don't want your uncle to have?"

msgctxt "8712"
msgid "いらないもの？　……なんでもいいのか？"
msgstr "unnecessary thing? ...... Anything is fine?"

msgctxt "8751"
msgid "うん！　なんでも！"
msgstr "Yup! what ever!"

msgctxt "8770"
msgid ""
"おっちゃんは知らないかもしれないけどさぁ、\n"
"オレ達子供って、\n"
"なんでもおもちゃにして遊べるんだぜ！"
msgstr ""
"You may not know the old man, but now, we kids can play with anything as a "
"toy!"

msgctxt "8869"
msgid "フッ、なるほどな。"
msgstr "Huh, I see."

msgctxt "10060"
msgid "少年"
msgstr "juvenile"

msgctxt "10065"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"
